articles.title: Airbus wins record order for 500 jets from India's IndiGo at Paris Air Show - The Associated Press
articles.description: PARIS (AP) — India's IndiGo airline is buying 500 passenger jets from European planemaker Airbus, the two companies said Monday, in a record-setting order that underscores surging demand for air travel fueled by the country's economic growth.
